item.title: CVE-2022-2410|2024-08-03T00:39:07.785Z -- unknown -- mtouch%20quiz
item.description: The mTouch Quiz WordPress plugin through 3.1.3 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
